  m_Text: 'In this Minigame your goal is to reel in your fish. You achieve this by
    keeping the fish withen the small bar. You can raise this bar by pressing space
    / left click. The bar naturally falls over time. The fish will move at random,
    the longer you keep it in the zone the more progress you make on the left bar.
    Fill the bar completly to catch your fish. '
